title: Add a Varchar Column With Collation in Mysql
tags: @zettel _method mysql
roam-id: 51509371-380c-4e90-add6-99be17a79f3b
type: text/markdown

``` sql
ALTER TABLE table_name ADD COLUMN column_name VARCHAR(length) COLLATE collation_name;
```

full example:

``` sql
ALTER TABLE bulk_coin_charging ADD COLUMN coin_completion_type VARCHAR(50) COLLATE utf8_turkish_ci;
```
